snippet.textDisplay: I know Wayne is the greatest rapper alive.He is actually an entertainer too; imagine that, you have to do more than Chopper Rap and be angry and whine(Im naming names Eminem💅😡) to be the greatest.I learned early in his career Wayne was inspired by Hall of Famer Missy Elliot.Very wise.You can't be angry all the time and talk fast and call yourself the greatest😐.Eminem is not unique to his region nor the fastest.Twista is actually faster than him💅💅💅.Tech Nine and Craig Mack also very fast.That is regional not special.Wayne is unique to his region though he does more than Bounce Music.If you strip Hip Hop of Funk, Punk, House,Rock, and Disco it is no longer Hip Hop.Wayne encompasses all of the elements that make Hip Hop.He knows the genre well.He is deserving of being a Hall of Famer.He can perform big events like the Superbowl.Do songs with Nu Metal artist.A style icon through decades.If the Grammys was not so rigged and favoritism he should have more and in more than one genre.Wayne is on par with New York rappers as a Southerner and Eminem is good as a Mid- Westerner but he is not in par with New Yorkers.There is a reason why he signed a New Yorker, always raps with New Yorkers, top list full of New Yorkers.😒.Wayne is "still the greatest rapper a-live; n** y'all died".
